data.description: This unique property features private views of Buena Vista Lake and park. You will feel like you are living in the country with all the convenience of everything Atlanta is known for. located in the popular and growing East Lake area you have easy access to East Atlanta Village, Emory, CDC, Midtown, Decatur, and major arteries. Walkable neighborhood, close to parks, schools, major roads. Master on main, updated kitchen, wonderful private backyard overlooking wooded  area and lake. Enjoy entertaining on the spacious deck and fenced in yard. The Terrace level includes a tremendous amoiunt of storage space as well as living areas including a full bath, office/bedroom/den flex space, a recentlky upgraded fully encapsulated basement with both separate exterior and interior access. This is the perfect space for an Great au-pair, mother-in-law suite, or rental unit. The possibilities are endless. Approximately =/- .3 acres.
